feat: add standalone MCP server for bridge tools (hr-eq8.5)

Create cmd/herald-bridges-mcp, a standalone MCP server binary that
exposes comms and health bridge tools via the MCP stdio protocol.
Reads COMMS_URL and HEALTH_URL env vars to connect to bridge services.
Implements JSON-RPC 2.0 MCP server protocol (initialize, tools/list,
tools/call). Includes tests and README documentation.

